Definition of Done

LD-STORAGE-02A is DONE when:

Legacy Doctor can format removable media larger than 32GB as FAT32 without Windows formatter or third-party FAT32 exe

formatter is deterministic and offline

formatter requires explicit destructive intent

formatter writes MBR + FAT32 structures correctly

formatter verifies its own output non-mutatingly

receipts are append-only and deterministic

safe selftests pass on disposable targets

one runner prints LEGACY_DOCTOR_FAT32_OWNED_ALL_GREEN

no interactive/manual post-fixes are required
